name: Origami Yoda's Paper Adventure (I made this when I was 10)
name_original: Origami Yoda's Paper Adventure (I made this when I was 10)
description:
I made this game when I was 10 years old and it's pretty bad by today's standards, but hey it's pretty ok for a 10-year-old.

I did this for absolutely no reason, except to show where I've come from.

I swear I make better games than this guys, you gotta believe me ;-;

If you're in the  0.00000000001 percentile of people who played this and maybe enjoyed it you can put your high scores in the comments, idrc.
